	animation: shorthand property.

	myanimation declared{}

	how to defined animation:  ?
	/*@font-face,@import*/
	
	@keyframes animationName{
		from{css props}
		to{css props}
	}
	/*0% - 100%*/
	@keyframes animationName{
		0%{css props}
		50%{css props}
		100%{css props}
	}

animation-fill-mode -
	none,both,forwards,backwards

